references: Related: CF 280116; Supersedes: Ord 103000; Amends: Ord 57142
summary: AN ORDINANCE renaming as the "Seattle Center Veterans Hall" the Seattle Center Veterans Annex at the Seattle Center, and amending Sections 1, 2, and of Ordinance 57142, and superseding Ordinance 103000 and all other ordinances to the extent inconsistent.
